Minister of Interior, Ogbeni Rauf Aregbesola on Tuesday commissioned 10 Ultra Modern Fire Service Trucks worth N1.8bn into service of the Federal Fire Service in Abuja. During the commission the minister said that the delivery of the new trucks was indeed further testimony of the determination of President Muhammadu Buhari to repositioning the Federal Fire Service. He also said that Federal Fire Service.responded to 2,615 Fire Calls, saved 724 lives and assets worth N1.629 trillion between June and October 2019 across the country. 